data.description: This very well-maintained, large 3-bedroom, 2-bath home is located on a beautiful 2.27-acre estate with a beautifully landscaped yard, featuring a paved circular driveway, a private backyard fire pit, nestled in a cozy lighted area perfect for friends and family get-togethers, or feeding the tamed squirrels, or rare bird watching. This home offers a large Florida room with high-volume vaulted ceilings connecting the kitchen, dining, and family areas, making it ideal for entertaining. The kitchen has like-new stainless steel appliances and a custom country pantry. Recent improvements include an Air Conditioner System, Water System, Flooring, Ceiling Fans, Roof, Interior/Exterior Paint, Remodeled Bathrooms, Custom Closets and Shelving, Custom Mud Room, Custom Laundry, Front Door, and so much more. This property is updated and ready to move in. In addition, the expansive screened lanai offers a great opportunity for you to relax and enjoy the beautiful Florida wildlife and landscape. The yard is fenced, and the location is great. Just around the corner from several new shopping centers.
